cast.overview: After failing to make it on Broadway, April returns to her hometown and reluctantly begins training a misfit group of young dancers for a competition.
cast.title: Feel the Beat

details.biography: Carina Battrick (born July 9, 2012) is a Canadian child actress. She is best known for her role as Caroline Cross in the Chucky series (2021-2024).  Her other roles include Young Henry Coles in Impulse, Young Tori Spelling in Broke and Famous, Young River in House of Chains, Jenny Lafferty in Under the Banner of Heaven, Harlow Heart in Blue's Clues & You, Sarah in Falling, and Michelle in Feel the Beat.
details.name: Carina Battrick
